title: CFB WEEK 10 SATURDAY
description:
Jen Lada, David Pollack, and Desmond Howard discuss the biggest storylines one day away from CFB Week 10 action. Is Michigan State on upset alert? Does Oregon or Ohio State need a win more this week? Find out all that and more here on the CFB Live Podcast!
